{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_12_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――{user}が星見プロに入社してすぐ",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、遙子さん、お疲れ様です。今日は……今から\n他の事務所のアイドルと合同レッスンですよね",
      "startTime": 8.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、わ、あ、あの、お疲れ様\nそ、そうなの、今からレッスン、行ってくるね",
      "startTime": 15.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "予定、知っててくれたんだ……\n麻奈ちゃんの、マネージャーなのに……！？",
      "startTime": 24.225034523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、私のこと気になって……いやいや\n同じ事務所のアイドルだからよ。勘違いしちゃダメ",
      "startTime": 32.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "後五分で事務所を出ないと遅れそうですね\n……遙子さん？　大丈夫ですか？",
      "startTime": 42.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "だっ、大丈夫！　そうだね、すぐ出ないとね\nありがとう、まっ、また明日……！",
      "startTime": 50.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、頑張って下さいねー！",
      "startTime": 54.5784815231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……何かぶつぶつ言ってた気がするけど\n俺、失礼なことしたかな……？",
      "startTime": 60.7332135913,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 56.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.1443544068
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.1443544068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "……という具合に、{user}君を意識して\n私ってば凄く浮かれてたのよね",
      "startTime": 70.0264497436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、俺に関することだとは……少し驚きました\nでもあの時は俺も仕事に必死で全然気付かなかったです",
      "startTime": 79.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.9874610898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "あははっ、いいのよ。意識はしていたけど\n今思えば、歳の近いお兄さんへの憧れだもん",
      "startTime": 88.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、{user}君って抜けてるところも\nあるって分かってからどんどん親しみやすくなったしね",
      "startTime": 95.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.0241734503
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.0241734503
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今日は俺が楽屋挨拶に同行させていただきます\n遙子さん……俺、頑張りますから！",
      "startTime": 105.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "うん、よろしくね、{user}君\n……そんなに緊張しなくて大丈夫よ",
      "startTime": 112.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.6639243442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、早速行きましょ。まずは\n{user}君、ノックを三回……そうそう",
      "startTime": 119.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5902.742322500004,
          "startTime": 121.5666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5833.333333399992,
          "startTime": 125.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.7809082983
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.7809082983
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こっ、こんにちは！　星見プロの佐伯遙子と\nマッ、マネージャーです！",
      "startTime": 129.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.9959420838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君……こういう業界では\n挨拶は、おはようございます、だよ……",
      "startTime": 134.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、あっ、すみません！\nおはようございます！",
      "startTime": 140.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.4875068026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます\n佐伯遙子です、本日はよろしくおねがいしましゅ！",
      "startTime": 144.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.3786855855
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.3786855855
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "覚えてますよ、その節は大変お世話になりました\nあの頃は、遙子さんに沢山教えてもらえて助かりました",
      "startTime": 155.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、年下の私が言うことでも\n嫌がらずに聞いて、お礼を言ってくれたよね",
      "startTime": 163.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.1076359111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "親しみやすくはなったけど、そういうところが\n凄くいいお兄さんで、信頼出来たんだよ",
      "startTime": 170.7334601424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.3479761122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "……そんな{user}君に言われて\n今でも忘れられないことがあるの",
      "startTime": 176.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "確か、凄く寒い冬の日で……\n私、その日はとっても落ち込んでいたのよ",
      "startTime": 182.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.6909467059
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.6909467059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、遙子さん……ど、どうしました？\nなんで泣いて……何があったんですか！？",
      "startTime": 193.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}君……ううん、なんでもないの",
      "startTime": 197.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "また、オーディションに受からなかっただけ……",
      "startTime": 202.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.0756325403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "たまにね、泣きたくなっちゃうんだ\n挫けたりはしないけど、悔しいじゃない……",
      "startTime": 209.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 221.0666656494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "私みたいな地味な子がアイドルなんて笑っちゃうよね\nでも、私……やっぱりアイドルになりたいの",
